<plot>After the untimely death of her father and step-mother, Sonia (Sadhana) is orphaned and lives with her aunt and paternal uncle (Mrs. and General Rajpal Singh). Sonia is plain-looking as her real mother, and often invites unappreciative, taunts, and critical remarks from her aunt and cousin-sister, Sheela (Azra). Sheela has a boyfriend, Dev Kumar Mehra (Joy Mukherji), and she plans to marry him. Fed-up of hearing frequent taunts and adverse remarks about her plain-looks, Sonia challenges Sheetal that she will make Dev fall in love with her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?345391</url></doc>
